  <body>
    <div class="container">
      #parse("common/header_top.vm") #parse("common/header.vm")
      <div class="content">
        <div class="wrap cc">
          #parse("common/left_menu_purchase.vm")
          <div class="user_right fl">
            <!-- 用户中心_主体内容_S -->
            <div class="indmain">
                <div class="path">
                    <p><a href="/purchase/index.html" class="color">采购中心 </a>&gt; 我的成长值 &gt; <span class="color">成长值说明</span></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                	<h3 class="fl">什么是成长值?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    ·  成长值是“我的医药网”会员通过购物、登录、升级所获得的。<a class="link" href="/purchase/growth/myGrowthValue.html">查看我的成长值</a><br /><br />
                    ·  累积的成长值总额决定会员级别，成长值越高会员等级越高，享受到的会员特权越大。<a class="link" href="/purchase/growth/myGrowthValue.html">查看会员级别介绍</a><br /><br />
                    ·  会员购物获取的成长值，可通过会员"成长值加成系数"加速。<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="link" onclick="top.frameScroll.doScrollTop($('#saber').offset().top,1)">查看加速系数介绍</a>
                </div>

                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                    <h3 class="fl">新人任务</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    <ul class="explain_ul cc">

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="" src="../../image/icon_integral_01.png">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color01">登录<span class="text">+20</span></p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    APP、PC 首次登录后获得<br />
                                    登录成功后发放
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="" src="../../image/icon_integral_02.png">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color02">企业认证<a class="text">+200</a></p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    完善企业基本信息和资质信息获得<br />
                                    审核通过后发放
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                    <h3 class="fl">日常任务</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    <ul class="explain_ul cc">

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_03.png" onclick="toPurchasse();">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color03">采购下单
                                	#if($!count2 > 0)
                            		<span class="text">+15</span>
                            		#else
                            		<a class="link" href="http://$!{wwwHostAndPort}/goods/quickPurchase.html">去完成</a>
                            		#end
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    PC下单按金额阶梯获得，使用APP、在线支付翻倍<br />
                                    以确认收货金额计算
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_04.png" onclick="toPurchasse();">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color04">多商家采购下单
                                	#if($!count1 > 1)
                            		<span class="text">+30</span>
                            		#else
                            		<a class="link" href="http://$!{wwwHostAndPort}/goods/quickPurchase.html">去完成</a>
                            		#end
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    每日在不同商家采购，额外奖励<br />
                                    确认收货后发放
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_05.png" onclick="toPurchasse();">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color05">在线支付
                                	#if($!count3 > 0)
                            		<span class="text">+30</span>
                            		#else
                            		<a class="link" href="http://$!{wwwHostAndPort}/goods/quickPurchase.html">去完成</a>
                            		#end
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    使用支付方式是在线支付每笔订单可<br />
                                    额外获得20成长值，同一商家每日只赠送一次；
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_06.png" onclick="showQRCode();">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color06">APP下单
                                	#if($!count4 > 0)
                            		<span class="text">+15*n</span>
                            		#else
                            		<a class="link" href="javascript:showQRCode();">去完成</a>
                            		#end
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    使用APP下单，每笔订单可额外获得10成长值<br />
                                    同一商家进行采购，每日只赠送1次
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                    <h3 class="fl">升级任务</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    <ul class="explain_ul cc">

                        <li>
                            <div class="img fl">
                                <img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_07.png">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                                <p class="top color07">会员升级</p>
                                <p class="mt10">
                                    系统自动升级后，额外奖励成长值，每个等级奖励不同<br />
                                    升级后立即奖励
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <a class="link" href="/purchase/growth/myGrowthValue.html">查看成长值介绍</a>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                	<h3 class="fl">扣除成长值</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    <ul class="explain_ul cc">
                    
                    	<li>
                        	<div class="img fl">
                            	<img class="shake shake-slow" src="../../image/icon_integral_09.png">
                            </div>
                            <div class="ctn fl">
                            	<p>
                                    会员级别有效期到期时会扣成长值
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <a class="link" href="/purchase/growth/myGrowthValue.html">查看成长值介绍</a>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="explain_title mt20">
                	<h3 class="fl">什么是成长值加成系数?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="explain_ctn">
                    ★ 成长值加成系数是根据您在我的医药网的购物行为评定的，由系统自动计算。
                    <img src="../../image/img_18.jpg" id="saber">
                </div>
                                
                <div class="integral_ps cc">
                	<div class="integral_ps_title">注</div>
                    <p>
                       1、成长值加系只限于新注册用户，在35天内按照加系标准完成前3单予以赠送。<br />
                       2、通过成长值加系获得额外奖励与订单奖励于确认收货后一并发放。<br />
                       3、相应额度的采购成长值*成长值加系倍数=该笔订单获得的成长值。<br />
                       4、如：您的订单确认收货时的金额为2000元，成长值加系倍数是1.2倍，那么您该笔订单的成长值是80*1.2=96。
                    </p>
                </div>
                
          </div>
          
          <!-- 用户中心_主体内容_E -->
